p.d: This weekly magazine series brings you the latest news and events from around the world of alternative sports; what’s new and what’s happening, who’s in and who’s out and who’s rewriting the rule book. With stunning images and editing, Action Sports World is the complete package for the ever growing youth demographic who are looking for the kind of high speed entertainment that only the world of action sports can provide.
